    "longBusinessSummary": "Sao Mai Group Corporation engages in the real estate, energy, human resources, aquaculture, construction, trade, and services businesses in Vietnam. The company involved in monetary intermediary activities; airline ticket agency; electricity transmission and distribution; hospitals and medical stations activities; wholesale of other household appliances; sauna, massage, spa, and similar health enhancing services; buying and selling souvenirs for tourists; production of paints, varnishes and similar paints and coatings; production of printing ink and mastics; manufacture of refractory products; and production of animal and vegetable oils and fats. It also provides construction of residential and non-residential houses; milling and producing raw flour; production of starch and products from starch; vocational training; and construction of mining projects services. In addition, the company engages in the wholesale of agricultural and forestry raw materials and live animals; consulting, brokerage, real estate auction, land use rights auction activities; construction of processing and manufacturing works; road construction detail; construction of transportation works; wholesale of cars and other motor vehicles; construction of veterinary, irrigation, underground structures, and water supply and drainage pipelines works; installation of water supply and drainage systems, heating and air conditioning systems; and wholesale of materials and other installation equipment. Further, the company buys and sells fish and seafood; and offers short-term accommodation services, inland aquaculture, seafood processing, and ground leveling services. Additionally, it involved in mining stone, sand, gravel, and clay; nursing home business; restaurants and catering services; installation of other construction systems; wholesale of beverages; and other entertainment activities. Sao Mai Group Corporation was founded in 1988 and is based in Long Xuyen, Vietnam.",
